text: Singhasan Sah Kalwar () is a Nepalese politician. He is a member of Provincial Assembly of Madhesh Province from People's Socialist Party, Nepal. Kalwar, a resident of Chhipahrmai Rural Municipality, was elected via 2017 Nepalese provincial elections from Parsa 4(B). ==References== Category:Living people Category:Nepalese politicians
title: Singhasan Sah Kalwar
